BBR Congestion Control
======================

This directory contains a BBR congestion control implementation derived
from the Hysteria project (github.com/apernet/hysteria), as vendored in
Xray-core (github.com/xtls/xray-core).

The original BBR algorithm was designed by Google for TCP. This Go
implementation was written by the Hysteria authors, porting from the
Chromium C++ codebase.

